{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"460dc6ce-7f63-4e88-8a23-5bbd7e2525bc","content":"**MSTest.Sdk 4.x dropped the VSTest compatibility layer by default.**\n\nIn 3.x, the SDK still shipped the VSTest adapter alongside the new Microsoft.Testing.Platform runner, so `vstest.console.exe` could discover tests. Starting with 4.0, only the new runner is included — `vstest.console` sees no adapter and finds zero tests.\n\nYou have two options:\n\n### Option A – Switch your CI to the new runner (recommended)\n\nReplace `vstest.console` with:\n\n```\ndotnet test TestProject.csproj\n```\n\nThe new platform is invoked automatically.\n\n### Option B – Re-enable the VSTest bridge\n\nAdd this property to your project file:\n\n```xml\n<EnableMicrosoftTestingExtensionsForVSTest>true</EnableMicrosoftTestingExtensionsForVSTest>\n```\n\nWant me to apply one of these fixes to your `TestProject.csproj`?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"3ceea41b-26cf-4572-9dd8-b923f47b8a57","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user upgraded from MSTest.Sdk/3.8.0 to 4.1.0 and vstest.console no longer discovers tests. I know about this breaking change.\n\nStarting with MSTest.Sdk 3.8.0, MSTest introduced the \"Microsoft.Testing.Platform\" (MTP) as the default test runner. However, the VSTest compatibility layer was still included by default in 3.x versions.\n\nIn MSTest.Sdk 4.0.0+, the VSTest compatibility layer is no longer included by default. The `EnableMicrosoftTestingExtensionsForVSTest` property (or similar) needs to be explicitly set, or you need to switch your CI pipeline to use `dotnet test` with the new testing platform instead of `vstest.console`.\n \nSo the core issue is that 4.x removed the VSTest bridge entirely, leaving only the new Microsoft.Testing.Platform runner. If the CI is still using `vstest.console.exe`, it won't find tests since the adapter is gone. The solution is either switching to `dotnet test` or explicitly re-enabling the VSTest compatibility layer in the project file.","outputTokens":571,"requestId":"E3EC:347368:240D841:2805ECB:6A05401A"},"id":"0d071d76-9bab-4fec-a004-497d6aaa09ff","timestamp":"2026-05-14T03:23:25.427Z","parentId":"b9168913-2db4-4ec4-af19-259b9c94e760"}
